      "text": "へぇ、本を選んだのね。『どんな礼儀知らずでも\n読めば変われる、大人のマナー100選』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you picked a book. “Anyone Who Is Badly Rude\nCan Change: 100 Manners for Adults”…",
        "id": ""
