      "text": "kanaってば、私達の方が年上なのに、態度悪いし\nケータリングの食べ方も汚いし、勉強が必要でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana is younger than us‚ but she’s rude‚\nand her table manners are atrocious. So she should learn‚ right?",
