      "text": "はぁ？　別にいいじゃない、実際ないんだから\nこの前なんて椅子の上にあぐらかいてたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What’s wrong with that? It’s true‚ she has no manners.\nThe other day‚ she was squatting on a chair!",
